<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Platform Admin Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #7c3aed 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 30px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .invite-card { background: white; padding: 25px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 5px solid #2563eb; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 15px 0; font-weight: 600; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; }
        .role-list { background: #f8fafc; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; }
        .expiry-warning { background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; color: #92400e; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>{{companyName}}</h1>
            <h2>Platform Admin Invitation</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>{{inviterName}} has invited you to join the platform admin team.</p>
            
            <div class="invite-card">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Welcome to the Platform Team!</h3>
                <p>You've been granted the following roles:</p>
                
                <div class="role-list">
                    {{#each roleCodes}}
                    <div style="margin: 5px 0;">‚Ä¢ {{this}}</div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
                
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="{{inviteUrl}}" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="expiry-warning">
                <strong>Important:</strong> This invitation expires on {{expiresAt}}. Please accept it before then.
            </div>
            
            <p>After accepting the invitation, you'll be able to:</p>
            <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>üè¢ Manage tenant accounts and subscriptions</li>
                <li>üí≥ Handle billing and payment issues</li>
                <li>üìä Access platform analytics and metrics</li>
                <li>üîß Configure platform settings</li>
                <li>üõ°Ô∏è Review audit logs and security events</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact the platform team.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>{{companyName}} Platform Administration</p>
            <p>This is an automated invitation. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>